cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper deals with the task of matching vectors from two data sources, specifically images and text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also makes use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
